thread.title_full: Car Hire Labs bewertet von Luca Guardamani

author: Luca Guardamani
title: Luca Guardamani
text:
I tried Car Hire Labs for a rent in Ciracao where prices are very high and insurance coverage for some big players on their website is USA style, so no CDW etc.
I found a very good price with all coverage I need and I received all the information about my focal points from customer service in a very short time.
